trans-unit.source: Throwable - the exception to throw from the method invocation on the proxy instance. The exception's type must be assignable either to any of the exception types declared in the throws clause of the interface method or to the unchecked exception types java.lang.RuntimeException or java.lang.Error. If a checked exception is thrown by this method that is not assignable to any of the exception types declared in the throws clause of the interface method, then an UndeclaredThrowableException containing the exception that was thrown by this method will be thrown by the method invocation on the proxy instance.
trans-unit.target: Throwable : la excepción para lanzar desde la invocación del método en la instancia del proxy. El tipo de excepción debe ser asignable a cualquiera de los tipos de excepción declarados en lacláusula throws del método de interfaz oa los tipos de excepción no java.lang.RuntimeException o java.lang.Error . Si este método lanza una excepción marcada que no se puede asignar a ninguno de los tipos de excepción declarados en lacláusula throws del método de interfaz,la invocación del método lanzaráuna UndeclaredThrowableException que contenga la excepción lanzada por este método en el instancia de proxy.

trans-unit.source: SecurityException - If the implementation requires to access the file, and a security manager is installed, and it denies an unspecified permission required by a file system provider implementation. If the file reference is associated with the default file system provider then the SecurityManager.checkRead(String) method is invoked to check read access to the file.

SecurityException - If the implementation requires to access the file, and a security manager is installed, and it denies an unspecified permission required by a file system provider implementation. If the file reference is associated with the default file system provider then the SecurityManager.checkRead(String) method is invoked to check read access to the file.
trans-unit.target: SecurityException : si la implementación requiere acceder al archivo y se instala un administrador de seguridad, y deniega un permiso no especificado requerido por la implementación de un proveedor de sistema de archivos. Si la referencia del archivo está asociada con el proveedor del sistema de archivos predeterminado,se invoca el método SecurityManager.checkRead(String) para verificar el acceso de lectura al archivo.

trans-unit.source: SecurityException - In the case of the default file system, the SecurityManager.checkRead(String) method is invoked to check read access if the file is opened for reading. The SecurityManager.checkWrite(String) method is invoked to check write access if the file is opened for writing
